markets.title: PSG vs Real Madrid Winner?
markets.rules_primary: If Tie wins the PSG vs Real Madrid professional Club World Cup soccer game originally scheduled for Jul 9, 2025 after 90 minutes plus stoppage time (does not include extra time or penalties), then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The following market refers to the PSG vs Real Madrid professional Club World Cup soccer game originally scheduled for Jul 9, 2025 after 90 minutes plus stoppage time (does not include extra time or penalties). If the game ends in a tie, the market called "Tie" resolves to Yes. If this game is postponed or delayed, the market will remain open and close after the rescheduled game/series has finished (within two years). If the cancelled game is not played or is rescheduled, the market will resolve to 33/33/33 for the market called "Tie" and both team markets.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire after a winner is declared.
